{"tid":1747041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推到候選人答應贏咗會幫手足】非建制派嘅最大共因數係幫手足唔係建制輸","createTime":"2019-11-23T04:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T03:37:43.000Z","uid":73980,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa3fd1e1deedb7b5a11f4bad430c8afde83d481","tid":1747041,"uid":73980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:38:21.000Z","msg":"唔少人嘈緊含唔含泛民，有班本土、獨派會俾人屈毛，又有班黃絲用「你唔係想建制贏呀？」做情緒勒索，呢樣又令人諗起泛民過去大量嘅不濟同背叛。<br />\n<br />\n好，依家唔洗嘈，距離選舉仲有一日，請所有支持呢場革命嘅候選人承諾贏咗會捐份薪津，或者用任何方式去幫所有被捕手足。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣本土獨派就唔算太含淚投票啦，黃絲又可以R到投啦，候選人又唔洗俾人指責食人血饅頭，一舉三得。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該候選人出聲，收曬出面所有分化post皮唔該</span>"},{"pid":"0cc43c005a70ef72a6fbb97610c193aae00c08b7","tid":1747041,"uid":73980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1d4baa90cb55d05e730849b0115eb5ce40973a0","tid":1747041,"uid":73980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b377a6caf561a000eb9a0670e5f3d5362a7a899","tid":1747041,"uid":73980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:52:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"769ab187ef52f9d2e2a870ba445ea59c206b6970","tid":1747041,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"我嗰邊有個承諾話會捐一半糧，如果icac 俾嘅話"},{"pid":"6ee1d1ea9c9033076c5efe6584c2500e965fb0ff","tid":1747041,"uid":73980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fe6f6e08cedc4224427d72219d5c7ef2d7317d9","tid":1747041,"uid":231933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:02:26.000Z","msg":"要 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建制</span></span> 和 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鄉黑</span></span> 大 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敗</span></span>！"},{"pid":"28400dab4a93d5113ac919b56a279